---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Lawrence Ghinea — Ghinea.io</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-[#090909] text-white font-sans antialiased">
    <main class="min-h-screen max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-5 py-14">
      <!-- Top bar -->
      <header class="flex items-center justify-between mb-10">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60 hover:text-white"
        >
          ← Back
        </a>
        <span class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40 uppercase">
          Personal · Context
        </span>
      </header>

      <!-- Hero -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(34px,5vw,56px)] font-semibold leading-[1.05] mb-3">
          Designer, builder, systems guy, dad.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/65 text-[16px] max-w-[640px] leading-relaxed">
          I like building calm, opinionated systems that make life feel a little less chaotic —
          for myself, my family, and the people who end up using the tools I ship.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Split: story + quick facts -->
      <section class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.5fr,1fr] mb-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/45 mb-3">
            The short version
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/78 text-[15px] leading-relaxed mb-3">
            I grew up obsessed with the internet, games and cameras. Eventually that turned into
            IT work — lots of tickets, lots of troubleshooting, lots of “this is broken, please fix it.”
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/78 text-[15px] leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Somewhere between photography, tech support and automation, I realized I’m happiest
            when I’m building systems that quietly run in the background while real life happens
            in the foreground.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/78 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
            Now I’m trying to turn that into a career I actually want to keep, instead of just
            another job I’m trying to escape from.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-[14px]">
          <div class="border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/45 mb-1">
              Currently
            </div>
            <p class="text-white/80">
              Building SaltySesh, hardening SeshBot™, and slowly replacing “corporate IT brain”
              with “builder / owner brain.”
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 bg-white/[0.02]">
            <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/45 mb-1">
              Anchors
            </div>
            <p class="text-white/80">
              Family, faith, long-term thinking, and not selling out my future just to look busy right now.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/45 mb-3">
          A quick timeline
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-[14px] text-white/75">
          <li><span class="text-white/40">Early 2020s ·</span> Corporate IT, tickets, systems, lots of “have you tried turning it off and on again.”</li>
          <li><span class="text-white/40">2024 ·</span> SaltySesh™ becomes real instead of theoretical. SeshBot™ starts as a side project and accidentally turns into a product.</li>
          <li><span class="text-white/40">Now ·</span> Building a small empire on purpose: photography, tools, and a future where I answer to my own calendar.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Closing -->
      <section class="mt-4 border-t border-white/10 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/45 mb-2">
            If you’re still reading
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-[14px] max-w-[420px]">
            You’re probably a builder, creator or systems person too. I’m always down to compare
            notes or trade ideas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="mailto:hello@ghinea.io?subject=Hey%20Lawrence"
          class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/10 text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-white/85 hover:bg-white/15"
        >
          Say hi
        </a>
      </section>

      <footer class="pt-6 mt-8 text-xs text-white/40 flex justify-between">
        <span>Ghinea.io · 2025</span>
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Back to main</a>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
